    {word:"Bane",pos:"noun",def:"A cause of great distress or annoyance.",bangla:"মহাদুর্ভোগের কারণ। যা জীবনে বারবার কষ্ট দেয়, তাকে bane বলে।",synonyms:["curse","plague","scourge"],antonyms:["blessing","benefit","boon"],examples:["Procrastination was the bane of his academic career.","Mosquitoes are the bane of summer evenings in the tropics."]},
