    {word:"Demagogue",pos:"noun",def:"A political leader who seeks support by appealing to desires and prejudices.",bangla:"জনমনে আবেগ ও কুসংস্কার ব্যবহার করে ক্ষমতা পাওয়ার চেষ্টা করা নেতা।",synonyms:["agitator","rabble-rouser","populist"],antonyms:["statesman","diplomat","peacemaker"],examples:["The demagogue inflamed tensions by scapegoating immigrants.","History shows how dangerous a skilled demagogue can be."]},
