  [
    {word:"Wanton",pos:"adjective",def:"Done in a deliberate and unprovoked way.",bangla:"উদ্দেশ্যমূলকভাবে ও বিনা কারণে করা।",synonyms:["deliberate","gratuitous","malicious"],antonyms:["justified","restrained","considerate"],examples:["The wanton destruction of the forest was condemned by environmentalists.","His wanton cruelty to animals shocked the entire community."]},
