    {word:"Zealot",pos:"noun",def:"A person who is fanatical about their cause.",bangla:"উগ্র ধর্মান্ধ বা মতান্ধ ব্যক্তি।",synonyms:["fanatic","extremist","radical"],antonyms:["moderate","skeptic","agnostic"],examples:["The political zealot refused to consider any opposing viewpoint.","Religious zealots can sometimes cause more harm than good in the name of faith."]},
